  "texts": [
    "This example underscores the need for sustained financial and institutional support for ongoing professional development in the dynamic field of STEM education.",
    "Exemplary Case 5.",
    "Reforming Pre-Service Teacher Training Programs (Jian et al. 2023, Chongqing and Guizhou).",
    "Jian et al. (2023) examined the reform of pre-service training curriculum systems for STEM teachers.",
    "The study proposed pathways for reform, such as project-based learning and cultivating practical wisdom, aimed at enhancing problem-solving skills and fostering interdisciplinary integration."
